## **README.md**  

```markdown
# Step-by-Step Guide to Install Node.js and NPM on Windows  

## 1️⃣ Install Node.js and NPM  
1. Download Node.js (LTS version) from [https://nodejs.org](https://nodejs.org).  
2. Run the `.msi` installer and follow the instructions.  
3. Verify installation:  
   ```sh
   node -v
   npm -v
   ```

## 2️⃣ Install Dependencies  
```sh
npm install
npm install express formidable
```

## 3️⃣ Run the Server  
```sh
node server.js
```

✅ Server runs at: **http://localhost:8080**  

## 4️⃣ Upload a File  
1. Open **http://localhost:8080** in your browser.  
2. Select a file and click **Upload**.  
3. The file will be saved in the specified directory.  

---
```

